  <summary date="2020-06-08T18:34:55Z" status="Introduced in House">Investor Choice Act of 2019

This bill prohibits broker-dealers and investment advisers from including mandatory arbitration, forum selection restrictions, or bans on class action suits in a customer or client agreement. Issuers of securities are also prohibited from mandating arbitration in a shareholder agreement.</summary>
